artifact.title: Effect Substitutability Study
artifact.name: Effect Substitutability Study
artifact.description: This artifact provides the necessary source code and data to reconstruct the results in our paper "Large-scale Study of Substitutability in the Presence of Effects". Specifically, this artifact provides the following: 1. source code of our 5 effect analyses provided as self-contained Boa programs 2. the raw output of running these 5 analyses on Boa's 2015 GitHub dataset 3. the list of randomly chosen cases (called examples herein) from our case study along with files of our analysis and categorizations each example.
